NOTES

1) SCRIPTS USAGE

- start locally connected client 
  /usr/local/urmetiotc_x86_64/bin/start_devices.sh <uid> <lport>

- stop locally client 
  /usr/local/urmetiotc_x86_64/bin/stop_devices.sh <uid> <lport>
  
- view locally mqtt connected elkron devices:
  /usr/local/urmetiotc_x86_64/bin/list_devices.sh

- view remotely connected to nod1-iotc mqtt devices:
  /usr/local/urmetiotc_x86_64/bin/list_devices.sh mntfrcud@nod1-iotc


